{"tid":1130396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴薄扶林道撞大廈外牆 上層玻璃粉碎","createTime":"2019-04-29T04:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T04:42:15.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f492a0d78f4a8603f27c0396d3daf49cbb6a2b","tid":1130396,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vijsH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vijsH2.png&h=8feef7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新巴薄扶林道撞大廈外牆 上層玻璃粉碎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGb1F29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGb1F29.png&h=d8e34f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上層多塊玻璃窗碎裂，一名乘客受傷。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpH8k3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpH8k3f.png&h=8da02cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士駛經彎位時撞外牆。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n一輛雙層新巴，早上10時許，沿西區薄扶林道行駛，至第二街附近一個上斜左彎，撞到大廈1樓外牆的石屎柱，左邊一列4塊玻璃窗全告碎裂，一名乘客被碎片割傷，報警後送院。巴士司機事後將車駛到前方，等候警方及巴士公司調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，要是巴士貼近馬路邊行駛，經過彎位時，與大廈相距不足半米：因此車長也會靠中間線行車。"},{"pid":"018e2363f67e84df193b1b3fbc99f02769a506f2","tid":1130396,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"大廈仲出過行人路咩？"},{"pid":"ad5dafc0b5dfec7cee6cb99d6bb9080181924d02","tid":1130396,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"行左半世紀都未出過事 呢條新手拖去打"},{"pid":"1be328658491603abdc3cd5276f999ed96de6561","tid":1130396,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/0aa/f1d/0aaf1d954ced72c31639a410f1f488761a2efdbd_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F0aa%2Ff1d%2F0aaf1d954ced72c31639a410f1f488761a2efdbd_n.jpg&h=76161ded&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}